1. This project is an Eclipse Project, use Eclipse IDE to open it


2. Feature List:

	1. Auth2.0 Authentication login
	2. View twitters, comment twitters, transfer twitters, Add Favorite List
	3. Support Pictures uploading with text 
	4. Support pictures viewing, support single-finger zoom-in zoom-out functionalities
	5. Support sqliteDataBase, store Blob images into db
	6. 

3. TBD 
	1. need to fix large picture


4. bin folder contains the APK file, U can download it and install it on your device
